name: CausIL
description: CausIL is an approach to estimate the causal graph for a cloud microservice system, where the nodes are the service-specific metrics while edges indicate causal dependency among the metrics. The approach considers metric variations for all the instances deployed in the system to build the causal graph and can account for auto-scaling decisions.
